cu.explanation_en: Setting the PHY log level to an invalid enum value 'invalid' will cause logging configuration errors during startup.

du.explanation_en: Setting the PHY log level to an invalid enum value 'invalid' will cause logging configuration errors during startup.
du.explanation_zh: 將 PHY 日誌等級設定為無效的枚舉值 'invalid' 會在啟動期間導致日誌配置錯誤。
